DBF-JDBC-Driver
Copyright 2026 The DBF-JDBC-Driver authors

This product includes software developed as a pure-Java JDBC driver for
DBF (dBASE / FoxPro / Clipper xBase) database files.

Portions of the xBase / Clipper binary format knowledge — version constants,
memo (.DBT/.FPT) block handling, and index/header layout facts — were derived
from the DANS dbf-lib project (https://github.com/DANS-KNAW/dans-dbf-lib),
which is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
